# Ğ´Ğ»Ñ Ğ»Ğ¾Ğ³Ğ¾Ğ²
import datetime
import inspect
# Ğ´Ğ»Ñ ÑĞ°Ğ¼Ğ¾Ğ¹ Ğ¿Ñ€Ğ¾Ğ³Ñ€Ğ°Ğ¼Ğ¼Ñ‹
from kivy.app import App
from kivy.uix.anchorlayout import AnchorLayout
from kivy.uix.boxlayout import BoxLayout
from kivy.uix.textinput import TextInput
from kivy.uix.dropdown import DropDown
from kivy.uix.button import Button
from kivy.uix.scrollview import ScrollView
from kivy.uix.label import Label
from kivy.properties import ListProperty
from kivy.clock import Clock

# Ğ¿Ñ€Ğ¾Ğ²ĞµÑ€ĞºĞ° 
def log_var(var_name, var_value, log_file="test4.log", func_name=None):
    """
    Ğ—Ğ°Ğ¿Ğ¸ÑÑ‹Ğ²Ğ°ĞµÑ‚ Ğ² Ğ»Ğ¾Ğ³-Ñ„Ğ°Ğ¹Ğ» Ğ½Ğ°Ğ·Ğ²Ğ°Ğ½Ğ¸Ğµ Ğ¿ĞµÑ€ĞµĞ¼ĞµĞ½Ğ½Ğ¾Ğ¹, ĞµÑ‘ Ğ·Ğ½Ğ°Ñ‡ĞµĞ½Ğ¸Ğµ Ğ¸ Ğ¸Ğ¼Ñ Ñ„ÑƒĞ½ĞºÑ†Ğ¸Ğ¸
    :param var_name: Ğ½Ğ°Ğ·Ğ²Ğ°Ğ½Ğ¸Ğµ Ğ¿ĞµÑ€ĞµĞ¼ĞµĞ½Ğ½Ğ¾Ğ¹ (ÑÑ‚Ñ€Ğ¾ĞºĞ°)
    :param var_value: Ğ·Ğ½Ğ°Ñ‡ĞµĞ½Ğ¸Ğµ Ğ¿ĞµÑ€ĞµĞ¼ĞµĞ½Ğ½Ğ¾Ğ¹
    :param log_file: Ğ¿ÑƒÑ‚ÑŒ Ğº Ğ»Ğ¾Ğ³-Ñ„Ğ°Ğ¹Ğ»Ñƒ (Ğ¿Ğ¾ ÑƒĞ¼Ğ¾Ğ»Ñ‡Ğ°Ğ½Ğ¸Ñ test4.log)
    :param func_name: Ğ¸Ğ¼Ñ Ñ„ÑƒĞ½ĞºÑ†Ğ¸Ğ¸ (ĞµÑĞ»Ğ¸ None, Ğ±ÑƒĞ´ĞµÑ‚ Ğ¾Ğ¿Ñ€ĞµĞ´ĞµĞ»ĞµĞ½Ğ¾ Ğ°Ğ²Ñ‚Ğ¾Ğ¼Ğ°Ñ‚Ğ¸Ñ‡ĞµÑĞºĞ¸)
    """
    timestamp = datetime.datetime.now().strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")
    
    # Ğ•ÑĞ»Ğ¸ Ğ¸Ğ¼Ñ Ñ„ÑƒĞ½ĞºÑ†Ğ¸Ğ¸ Ğ½Ğµ ÑƒĞºĞ°Ğ·Ğ°Ğ½Ğ¾, Ğ¿Ñ‹Ñ‚Ğ°ĞµĞ¼ÑÑ Ğ¾Ğ¿Ñ€ĞµĞ´ĞµĞ»Ğ¸Ñ‚ÑŒ Ğ°Ğ²Ñ‚Ğ¾Ğ¼Ğ°Ñ‚Ğ¸Ñ‡ĞµÑĞºĞ¸
    if func_name is None:
        try:
            # ĞŸĞ¾Ğ»ÑƒÑ‡Ğ°ĞµĞ¼ Ğ¸Ğ¼Ñ Ğ²Ñ‹Ğ·Ñ‹Ğ²Ğ°ÑÑ‰ĞµĞ¹ Ñ„ÑƒĞ½ĞºÑ†Ğ¸Ğ¸ (2 ÑƒÑ€Ğ¾Ğ²Ğ½Ñ Ğ²Ñ‹ÑˆĞµ Ğ² ÑÑ‚ĞµĞºĞµ Ğ²Ñ‹Ğ·Ğ¾Ğ²Ğ¾Ğ²)
            func_name = inspect.currentframe().f_back.f_back.f_code.co_name
        except:
            func_name = "unknown"
    
    log_message = f"[{timestamp}] [{func_name}] {var_name} = {repr(var_value)}\n"
    
    with open(log_file, "a", encoding="utf-8") as f:
        f.write(log_message)

class SearchBox(BoxLayout):
    suggestions = ListProperty([])
    
    def __init__(self, **kwargs):
        super(SearchBox, self).__init__(**kwargs)
        self.orientation = 'vertical'
        
        # ĞšĞ¾Ğ½Ñ‚ĞµĞ¹Ğ½ĞµÑ€ Ğ´Ğ»Ñ Ğ¿Ğ¾Ğ»Ñ Ğ¿Ğ¾Ğ¸ÑĞºĞ°
        search_container = AnchorLayout(
            anchor_x='center',
            anchor_y='top',
            size_hint=(1, None),
            height=40
        )
        
        self.search_input = TextInput(
            hint_text='Ğ’Ğ²ĞµĞ´Ğ¸Ñ‚Ğµ Ğ¿Ğ¾Ğ¸ÑĞºĞ¾Ğ²Ñ‹Ğ¹ Ğ·Ğ°Ğ¿Ñ€Ğ¾Ñ...',
            size_hint=(1, None),
            height=40
        )
        self.search_input.bind(text=self.on_text)
        search_container.add_widget(self.search_input)
        self.add_widget(search_container)
        
        # Ğ’Ñ‹Ğ¿Ğ°Ğ´Ğ°ÑÑ‰Ğ¸Ğ¹ ÑĞ¿Ğ¸ÑĞ¾Ğº (Ğ±ĞµĞ· Ğ¾Ğ³Ñ€Ğ°Ğ½Ğ¸Ñ‡ĞµĞ½Ğ¸Ğ¹)
        self.dropdown = DropDown()
        self.dropdown.bind(on_select=lambda i, x: (
            setattr(self.search_input, 'text', x),
            self.update_search_results(x)
        ))
        
        # ĞĞ±Ğ»Ğ°ÑÑ‚ÑŒ Ñ€ĞµĞ·ÑƒĞ»ÑŒÑ‚Ğ°Ñ‚Ğ¾Ğ²
        self.scroll = ScrollView(size_hint=(1, 1))
        self.add_widget(self.scroll)
        
        self.results_layout = BoxLayout(
            orientation='vertical',
            size_hint_y=None,
        )
        self.results_layout.bind(minimum_height=self.results_layout.setter('height'))
        self.scroll.add_widget(self.results_layout)
        
        self.all_data = [
            "Python Ğ¿Ñ€Ğ¾Ğ³Ñ€Ğ°Ğ¼Ğ¼Ğ¸Ñ€Ğ¾Ğ²Ğ°Ğ½Ğ¸Ğµ",
            "Kivy Ñ€Ğ°Ğ·Ñ€Ğ°Ğ±Ğ¾Ñ‚ĞºĞ° Ğ¿Ñ€Ğ¸Ğ»Ğ¾Ğ¶ĞµĞ½Ğ¸Ğ¹",
            "Android Ğ¿Ñ€Ğ¸Ğ»Ğ¾Ğ¶ĞµĞ½Ğ¸Ñ Ğ½Ğ° Python",
            "Ğ˜Ğ·ÑƒÑ‡ĞµĞ½Ğ¸Ğµ Kivy Ğ´Ğ»Ñ Ğ½Ğ°Ñ‡Ğ¸Ğ½Ğ°ÑÑ‰Ğ¸Ñ…",
            "ĞŸÑ€Ğ¸Ğ¼ĞµÑ€Ñ‹ Kivy Ğ¿Ñ€Ğ¸Ğ»Ğ¾Ğ¶ĞµĞ½Ğ¸Ğ¹",
            "Ğ Ğ°Ğ±Ğ¾Ñ‚Ğ° Ñ Ğ±Ğ°Ğ·Ğ°Ğ¼Ğ¸ Ğ´Ğ°Ğ½Ğ½Ñ‹Ñ… Ğ² Python",
            "ĞœĞ¾Ğ±Ğ¸Ğ»ÑŒĞ½Ğ°Ñ Ñ€Ğ°Ğ·Ñ€Ğ°Ğ±Ğ¾Ñ‚ĞºĞ° Ñ Kivy",
            "ĞœĞ¾Ğ±Ğ¸Ğ»ÑŒĞ½Ğ°Ñ Ñ€Ğ°Ğ·Ñ€Ğ°Ğ±Ğ¾Ñ‚ĞºĞ° Ñ Kivy",
            "ĞœĞ¾Ğ±Ğ¸Ğ»ÑŒĞ½Ğ°Ñ Ñ€Ğ°Ğ·Ñ€Ğ°Ğ±Ğ¾Ñ‚ĞºĞ° Ñ Kivy",
            "ĞœĞ¾Ğ±Ğ¸Ğ»ÑŒĞ½Ğ°Ñ Ñ€Ğ°Ğ·Ñ€Ğ°Ğ±Ğ¾Ñ‚ĞºĞ° Ñ Kivy",
            "ĞœĞ¾Ğ±Ğ¸Ğ»ÑŒĞ½Ğ°Ñ Ñ€Ğ°Ğ·Ñ€Ğ°Ğ±Ğ¾Ñ‚ĞºĞ° Ñ Kivy",
            "ĞœĞ¾Ğ±Ğ¸Ğ»ÑŒĞ½Ğ°Ñ Ñ€Ğ°Ğ·Ñ€Ğ°Ğ±Ğ¾Ñ‚ĞºĞ° Ñ Kivy",
            "ĞœĞ¾Ğ±Ğ¸Ğ»ÑŒĞ½Ğ°Ñ Ñ€Ğ°Ğ·Ñ€Ğ°Ğ±Ğ¾Ñ‚ĞºĞ° Ñ Kivy",
            "ĞœĞ¾Ğ±Ğ¸Ğ»ÑŒĞ½Ğ°Ñ Ñ€Ğ°Ğ·Ñ€Ğ°Ğ±Ğ¾Ñ‚ĞºĞ° Ñ Kivy",
            "ĞœĞ¾Ğ±Ğ¸Ğ»ÑŒĞ½Ğ°Ñ Ñ€Ğ°Ğ·Ñ€Ğ°Ğ±Ğ¾Ñ‚ĞºĞ° Ñ Kivy",
            "ĞœĞ¾Ğ±Ğ¸Ğ»ÑŒĞ½Ğ°Ñ Ñ€Ğ°Ğ·Ñ€Ğ°Ğ±Ğ¾Ñ‚ĞºĞ° Ñ Kivy",
            "GUI Ğ¿Ñ€Ğ¸Ğ»Ğ¾Ğ¶ĞµĞ½Ğ¸Ñ Ğ½Ğ° Python"
        ]
        
        self.placeholder = Label(
            text="Ğ’Ğ²ĞµĞ´Ğ¸Ñ‚Ğµ Ğ·Ğ°Ğ¿Ñ€Ğ¾Ñ Ğ´Ğ»Ñ Ğ¿Ğ¾Ğ¸ÑĞºĞ°",
            size_hint_y=None,
            height=40,
            color=(0.5, 0.5, 0.5, 1),
            halign='center'
        )
        self.results_layout.add_widget(self.placeholder)
    
    def on_text(self, instance, value):
        Clock.unschedule(self.update_suggestions)
        # Ğ¡Ğ½Ğ°Ñ‡Ğ°Ğ»Ğ° Ğ¾Ğ±Ğ½Ğ¾Ğ²Ğ»ÑĞµĞ¼ suggestions, Ğ·Ğ°Ñ‚ĞµĞ¼ Ñ€ĞµĞ·ÑƒĞ»ÑŒÑ‚Ğ°Ñ‚Ñ‹
        self.update_suggestions_immediately(value)
        Clock.schedule_once(self.update_suggestions, 0.2)
    
    def update_suggestions_immediately(self, value):
        """ĞĞµĞ¼ĞµĞ´Ğ»ĞµĞ½Ğ½Ğ¾Ğµ Ğ¾Ğ±Ğ½Ğ¾Ğ²Ğ»ĞµĞ½Ğ¸Ğµ suggestions Ğ±ĞµĞ· Ğ·Ğ°Ğ´ĞµÑ€Ğ¶ĞºĞ¸"""
        query = value.lower().strip()
        if not query:
            self.suggestions = []
            return

        self.suggestions = [item for item in self.all_data if query in item.lower()]
        self.update_search_results(query)

    def update_suggestions(self, dt):
        query = self.search_input.text.lower().strip()
        self.dropdown.dismiss()

        if not query:
            return
            
        # ĞŸĞ¾Ğ»ÑƒÑ‡Ğ°ĞµĞ¼ Ğ’Ğ¡Ğ• ÑĞ¾Ğ²Ğ¿Ğ°Ğ´ĞµĞ½Ğ¸Ñ Ğ´Ğ»Ñ Ğ²Ñ‹Ğ¿Ğ°Ğ´Ğ°ÑÑ‰ĞµĞ³Ğ¾ ÑĞ¿Ğ¸ÑĞºĞ°
        self.suggestions = [item for item in self.all_data if query in item.lower()]
        self.dropdown.clear_widgets()
        
        # Ğ¡Ğ¾Ğ·Ğ´Ğ°ĞµĞ¼ ĞºĞ½Ğ¾Ğ¿ĞºĞ¸ Ğ´Ğ»Ñ Ğ²ÑĞµÑ… ÑĞ¾Ğ²Ğ¿Ğ°Ğ´ĞµĞ½Ğ¸Ğ¹
        for suggestion in self.suggestions:
            btn = Button(
                text=suggestion,
                size_hint_y=None,
                height=40
            )
            btn.bind(on_release=lambda btn: self.dropdown.select(btn.text))
            self.dropdown.add_widget(btn)
        
        if self.suggestions:
            self.dropdown.open(self.search_input)

    def update_search_results(self, query):
        self.results_layout.clear_widgets()

        if not query.strip():
            self.results_layout.add_widget(self.placeholder)
            return
            
        # Ğ˜ÑĞ¿Ğ¾Ğ»ÑŒĞ·ÑƒĞµĞ¼ Ñ‚Ğµ Ğ¶Ğµ Ñ€ĞµĞ·ÑƒĞ»ÑŒÑ‚Ğ°Ñ‚Ñ‹, Ñ‡Ñ‚Ğ¾ Ğ¸ Ğ´Ğ»Ñ dropdown
        results = self.suggestions
        
        if not results:
            self.results_layout.add_widget(Label(
                text="ĞĞ¸Ñ‡ĞµĞ³Ğ¾ Ğ½Ğµ Ğ½Ğ°Ğ¹Ğ´ĞµĞ½Ğ¾",
                size_hint_y=None,
                height=40,
                color=(0.7, 0.3, 0.3, 1),
                halign='center'
            ))
        else:
            for result in results:
                self.results_layout.add_widget(Button(
                    text=result,
                    size_hint_y=None,
                    height=40,
                    background_color=(0.9, 0.9, 0.9, 1)
                ))

class SearchApp(App):
    def build(self):
        return SearchBox()

if __name__ == '__main__':
    SearchApp().run()

import pygame
from platforma import Platforma
SZEROKOSC=1024
WYSOKOSC=800
ekran=pygame.display.set_mode([SZEROKOSC,WYSOKOSC])
obraz_tla=pygame.image.load('images/background.png')
status_gry=True
platforma=Platforma()
while status_gry:
    for zdarzenie in pygame.event.get():
        if zdarzenie.type==pygame.QUIT:
            status_gry=False
        elif zdarzenie.type==pygame.KEYDOWN:
            if zdarzenie.key==pygame.K_ESCAPE:
                status_gry=False
    keys=pygame.key.get_pressed()#pobieranie wciÅ›niÄ™tych(i tzymanych)
    if keys[pygame.K_a] or keys[pygame.K_LEFT]:
        platforma.przesun(-1)
    if keys[pygame.K_d] or keys[pygame.K_RIGHT]:
        platforma.przesun(1)

    ekran.blit(obraz_tla,(0,0))
    ekran.blit(platforma.obraz,platforma.rect)
    pygame.display.flip()
pygame.quit()
